sections.text:
77-2701.40.Tax Commissioner, defined.

Tax Commissioner means the Tax Commissioner of the State of Nebraska.

SourceLaws 1992, LB 871, § 22;R.S.1943, (1996), § 77-2702.21;Laws 2003, LB 282, § 44.
